' *** FACULTY.LST ***                                  2nd GFA-Manual, page 6-9
FUNCTION faculty(number)
  '
  ' *** Return faculty of number&
  ' *** If number& < 450, result can be PRINTed normally
  ' *** Larger faculties can be calculated; and printed with PRINT USING
  ' *** If number& > 862, GFA aborts with overflow-error
  '
  LOCAL fac#,i
  fac#=1
  FOR i=1 TO number
    MUL fac#,i
  NEXT i
  RETURN fac#
ENDFUNC
' *****
'
